{
  "stem": "10353.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So they confiscated the papers and they lined us up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then they started to sort of segregate people by age.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they lined us up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And again, under heavy, heavy guards with the gendarmes and this Arrow Cross, they marched us to a building.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was called Teleki Square, T-E-L-E-K-I Square.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was a multi-story building and they marched us in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And this was on a Sunday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "On Monday morning, I was-- this time I was very unlucky, because they put me on the third floor and some people were on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "On Monday morning, Wallenberg came with a bus and demanded that all the Swedish-- all the people there with Swedish papers should be released.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But people didn't have anymore the Swedish papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But nonetheless, they broke open by force the portals and they jammed into the bus, so anybody that was on the ground floor got first shot.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "By the time I came down from the third floor, I was already caught in a trap.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I couldn't go out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Some people escaped and Wallenberg took them away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Around 10 o'clock or so, we were ordered to march down and to line up, which we did.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We were lined up and we started to be marched toward the railway station.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And the railway station-- we arrived at the railway station still under heavy guard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We were lined up in rows and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were broken up in groups of 70 and we marched-- we were put in 70 people per freight car.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All men.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All men.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Young men, middle-aged men.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this procedure was taking on practically most of the day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And towards nightfall, the train moved out.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
